attributes.title: Official Trailer - Season 4
attributes.caption: Camp Campbell has a different feel to it these days thanks to Mr. Campbell hanging around to do his mandatory community service. But rest assured, it’s still the same chaotic mess it’s always been! Actually, it might be even worse…
attributes.description: Gooooooood morning, campers! Camp Campbell has a slightly different feel to it these days thanks to Mr. Campbell hanging around to do his mandatory community service. But rest assured, it’s still the same chaotic mess it’s always been! Actually, it might be even worse… or better, depending upon who you ask.

attributes.title: Camp Camp Bloopers
attributes.caption: When we F up Camp Camp, we really F up Camp Camp. Send the kids out of the room and check out the official Camp Camp blooper reel. New season starts June 1, only on Rooster Teeth.
attributes.description: When we F up Camp Camp, we really F up Camp Camp. Send the kids out of the room and check out the official Camp Camp blooper reel. New season starts June 1, only on Rooster Teeth.

attributes.title: Camp Campbell Wants YOU!
attributes.caption: ​Hey kids! Do you want to have FUN this summer?! Then you gotta come on down to Camp Campbell! We've got everything you could ever want in a summer camp, and some stuff you didn't even think you wanted (but still have to do)!
attributes.description: Hey kids! Do you want to have FUN this summer?! Then you gotta come on down to Camp Campbell! We've got everything you could ever want in a summer camp, and some stuff you didn't even think you wanted (but still have to do)!Hey parents! Do you have the money spend in order to buy some peace and quiet for a month or so?! Then Camp Campbell will happily take your kids off your hands so you can escape to Cancun or just have a clean house for longer than an afternoon! CALL TODAY!!

attributes.caption: Camp Camp is back for a new season of dysfunctional summer fun! Join Max, Nikki, and the rest of the campers on new adventures as they try to survive the annoyingly cheerful counselor David.
